" Toggle fold/unfold
nnoremap <Return>  za

" Temporarily turn of search highlighting
nnoremap <Leader>/  :nohlsearch<CR>

" Paste from clipboard (Inserting ^-<Key> can be done using C-q)
inoremap <C-V>  <Esc>"*pa

" Window navigation
nnoremap <M-h>  <C-w>h
nnoremap <M-j>  <C-w>j
nnoremap <M-k>  <C-w>k
nnoremap <M-l>  <C-w>l
